  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0ddb\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0da7 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dac \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddc\u0dca\u0db0\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A silent protest against attacking the doctor",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The entire staff of the hospital, including the doctors and nurses, engaged in a peaceful protest in front of the hospital today (21) condemning the attack on a doctor who was on duty at the Polonnaruwa Jayanthipura Village and Rehabilitation Hospital yesterday afternoon (21).",
        "Due to this inhuman attack, the entire staff of the hospital, including doctors and nurses, are away from their duties and the hospital has been temporarily closed.",
        "Dr. Suranga Hewawitharana, Medical Officer in Charge of the Jayantipura Rural and Rehabilitation Hospital stated that all the patients who were in the hospital have been transferred to other hospitals.",
        "It has been revealed that the person who was arrested by the Minneriya Police on suspicion of assaulting the doctor is a resident of Jayantipura, Nagapokuna area."
      ],
